title: Recap: Tech shut out by Baylor - Texas Tech Red Raiders - TexasTech.com
content: Recap: Tech shut out by Baylor - Texas Tech Red Raiders  TexasTech.com
description: WACO, Texas – Texas Tech (21-23, 4-10) was shutout for the second straight game, falling 4-0 to Baylor (25-18, 4-7) Saturday afternoon at Getterman Stadium.
